strings.Value: "Irovetti is a major threat. We need to move fast. The people are worried."
"This is precisely why plebeians shouldn't know how to read. Propaganda leaflets wouldn't confuse people, if there weren't anyone to read them."
"The quiet one is right. The longer we sit pretty, the more violent the riots get."
